        </li>
                <li>
            <span class="who">
                <span class="">Hildegarde Franz</span>:
            </span>
            <span class="utterance" who="#franzH" start="1036.043" end="x">They have . . . that [the permission] I got, too.</span>
        </li>
                <li>
            <span class="who">
                <span class="">David Boder</span>:
            </span>
            <span class="utterance" who="#boderD" start="1037.684" end="x">Yes. So that was safe.</span>
        </li>
                <li>
            <span class="who">
                <span class="">Hildegarde Franz</span>:
            </span>
            <span class="utterance" who="#franzH" start="1039.512" end="x">Yes, that was safe. But of the furnishings of my apartment, I have lost very, very much.</span>
