                <span class="">Hildegarde Franz</span>:
            </span>
            <span class="utterance" who="#franzH" start="1195.444" end="x">Eighteen thousand people were dragged off from <a class="placename" href="#vothC110" type="camp">Theresienstadt</a> to Poland.</span>
        </li>
                <li>
            <span class="who">
                <span class="">David Boder</span>:
            </span>
